<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <% include base/link.ejs %>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container ">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="hr-40"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="panel panel-default box-shadow border-none border-radius">
        <div class="panel-body">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 .col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                        <div class="page-header">
                            <h2><a href="/blogs">LIGHTCOLORS</a><br>
                                <small>node for blog</small>
                            </h2>
                        </div>
                        <% include base/crumb.ejs %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 ">
                        <div id="" class="">
                            <!--标题-->
                            <div class="page-header">
                                <h4><%= post.title %><br></h4>
                            </div>
                            <!--提示信息-->
                            <div class="">
                                <span class="label label-success inline-block"><i
                                            class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></i> <%= post.date %></span><span
                                        class="label label-info inline-block"><i
                                            class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i> <%= post.name %></span><span
                                        class="label label-success inline-block"><i
                                            class="glyphicon glyphicon-paperclip"></i> <%= post.category %></span><span
                                        class="label label-info inline-block"><i
                                            class="glyphicon glyphicon-eye-open"></i> <%= post.pv %></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="hr-20"></div>
                            <!--内容-->
                            <div class=""><%- post.post %></div>
                            <div class="hr-40"></div>
                            <div class="underline"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-12">
                        <div class="page-header">
                            <h4>评论
                                <small class="badge">node for blog</small>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <form>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <font>*</font><label for="commentEmail">Email address</label>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control" name="commentEmail" id="commentEmail"
                                       placeholder="Your email">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <font>*</font><label for="commentName">Your name</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="commentName" id="commentName"
                                       placeholder="Your name">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <font>*</font><label for="commentContent">Content</label>
                                <textarea rows="4" class="form-control" name="commentContent" id="commentContent"
                                          placeholder="Content"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="checkbox">
                                <label>
                                    <input type="checkbox"> Remember me
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-12">
                        <div class="page-header">
                            <h4>评论列表
                                <small class="badge">12</small>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div class="media">
                            <div class="media-left">
                                <a href="#">
                                    <img class="media-object" data-src="holder.js/64x64" alt="64x64"
                                         src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
                                         data-holder-rendered="true" style="width: 64px; height: 64px;">
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="media-body">
                                <h4 class="media-heading">Media heading</h4>
                                <small>Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla. Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante
                                sollicitudin commodo. Cras purus odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus viverra
                                turpis. Fusce condimentum nunc ac nisi vulputate fringilla. Donec lacinia congue felis
                                in faucibus.</small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hr-40"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <% include footer.ejs %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

<script type="text/javascript" src="http://libs.useso.com/js/jquery/2.0.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="javascripts/account.js"></script>
<script src="/javascripts/ajax.js"></script>
